detail.name: Son Goku (Mini) : DA
detail.effect: [When Attacking] Discard 1 card from your hand : If your Leader has <DA> in its card name, choose up to 1 Battle Card in your opponent's Battle Area and it gets -20000 power for the turn.

detail.name: 孫悟空(ミニ)：DA
detail.effect: 【アタック時】自分の手札1枚を捨てる：自分のリーダーがカード名に「DA」を含む場合、相手のバトルエリアのバトルカード1枚までを選び、このターン中、パワー-20000。
